title: 97: Business Broads with Jenna Rainey
itunes:title: 97: Business Broads with Jenna Rainey
description:
The Broads are joined by the amazing CEO/Product Designer/Watercolor artist/author badass business woman and mother extraordinare - Jenna Rainey! They chat how to get your start, the fear of failure, the beauty in mistakes, getting paid, protecting yourself financially, balance, taking care of yourself, and much more!
